
=Bio=

"Marco Giustini (Roma, 1963) aka magius, is an italian activist involved in different social, political and ecological movements since his early age. From alterglobal, to ethical buying, monetary reform, independent media, indignados, occupy and soon. He was the co-founder of FAZ project (www.faz.im), he's involved in the ecological movement against waste management, Indymedia Italia, social occupied centers and in the last five years he was also a local MEP."


